===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|zoology}} A [[larval]] [[entozoön]] in the form of a [[subglobular]] or oval [[vesicle]], or [[hydatid]], filled with fluid, sometimes found in the tissues of man and the lower animals; -- so called from the absence of a head or visible organs on the vesicle. These cysts are the [[immature]] stages of certain [[tapeworm]]s. Also applied to similar cysts of different origin.

